<title>94名小学生肠胃不适被送医，广东陆丰通报</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+94%E5%90%8D%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E8%82%A0%E8%83%83%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E5%8C%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E9%99%86%E4%B8%B0%E9%80%9A%E6%8A%A5</link>
